panels.description:
Load failure count - Total number of times the cache lookup method failed to compile a new script for the session with engine.

Load failure rate - Ratio of script compilation attempts that failed for the session with engine.
panels.title: Cache Load Failure

panels.description:
Eviction Count - Number of times a script compiled to a class has been evicted from the cache for the session with engine.

Eviction weight - Sum of the weights of evicted entries from the class cache for the session with engine.
panels.title: Cache Eviction

panels.description: Number of compilations that extended beyond the expected compilation time for the session with engine.
panels.title: Cache Long Run compilation

panels.description:
Hit count - Number of compilations that extended beyond the expected compilation time for the session with engine.

Hit rate - Hit rate of the class cache for the session with engine.
panels.title: Cache Hit

panels.description:
Miss count - Total number of times the cache lookup method returned a newly compiled script for the session with engine.

Miss Rate - Ratio of script compilation attempts that were misses for the session with engine.
panels.title: Cache Miss
